These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-1::.
3 different games are played: bridge, canasta, snooker
3 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, rat
1. the owner of the rat is somewhere between the person playing bridge and the owner of the ferret##7
2. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5
3. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3   |
| Game   | snooker | canasta | bridge |
| Pet           | ferret  | rat     | bird  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-2::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, electronic, reggae
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, dunhill, aristoff
1. the bongani-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of country is somewhere between the fan of reggae and the dunhill-smoker##7
3. the bongani-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | country | reggae |
| Cigar     | dunhill       | aristoff     | bongani |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, mirinda, water
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, baking, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the person who's hobby is gardening##7
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |   3    |
| Beverage    | coffee | mirinda | water  |
| Hobby   | woodworking  | baking  | gardening |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  project-manager, scientist, teacher
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, scooter, roller
1. the project-manager is somewhere between the person driving the roller and the scientist##7
2. the person driving the scooter is not the project-manager##6
3. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |      3      |
| Job           | scientist | project-manager | teacher     |
| Transport   | scooter    | trike          | roller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-5::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, hip-hop, salsa
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, oliveros, prince
1. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere between the prince-smoker and the fan of hip-hop##7
2. the havana-smoker is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | disco      | salsa     | hip-hop   |
| Cigar     | prince | oliveros | havana |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-6::.
There 3 different types of food: blueberry, papaya, cabbage
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, japanese, pakistani
1. the colombian is on the left or right of the japanese##3
2. the japanese is somewhere to the left of the colombian##5
3. the person eating papaya is on the right of the pakistani##1
4. the person eating papaya is somewhere between the pakistani and the person eating blueberry##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Food   | cabbage    | papaya     | blueberry     |
| Nationality   | pakistani | japanese | colombian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-7::.
3 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish, rat
House: palace, colonial, futuristic
1. the futuristic house is on the right of the palace house##1
2. the futuristic house is somewhere between the owner of the goat and the palace house##7
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Pet     | rat       | goldfish      | goat       |
| House   | palace | futuristic | colonial |

