2. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere between the montecristo-smoker and the electrician##7
3. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Job           | entrepreneur | doctor  | electrician |
| Cigar   | montecristo      | pall-mall | oliveros      |

