.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-9::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, horror, disaster
The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, manager, teacher
1. the teacher is not the person watching disaster movies##6
2. the manager is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the doctor is somewhere between the manager and the person watching horror movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | disaster | mystery   |
| Job     | teacher    | doctor  | manager |

