.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-10::.
House: tower, colonial, townhouse
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, skiing, tennis
1. the tower house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is the colonial house##1
3. the townhouse house is somewhere between the colonial house and the person who's sport is skiing##7

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| House   | colonial   | townhouse    | tower |
| Sport      | tennis | badminton | skiing |

