.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-11::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, rock-climbing, traveling
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, bike, jet-ski
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere between the person driving the bike and the person driving the snowmobile##7
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is not the person who's hobby is traveling##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Hobby         | traveling | fishing | rock-climbing |
| Transport   | bike    | jet-ski    | snowmobile         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-12::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: pink, emerald, blood-red
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, superhero, zombie
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the person watching superhero movies and the person who likes pink##7
3. the person who likes emerald is somewhere to the right of the person watching scientific movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3     |
| Color          | pink  | blood-red       | emerald     |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | scientific | superhero |

