.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-13::.
City: venice, edinburgh, san-francisco
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, house, rock
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is somewhere between the fan of electronic and the fan of rock##7
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
3. the fan of house is somewhere between the fan of electronic and the person traveling to edinburgh##7
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the fan of house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |  3   |
| City      | venice     | san-francisco | edinburgh |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | house    | rock |

