2. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hannover##5
3. the person traveling to prague is somewhere between the french and the person traveling to hamburg##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |
| Nationality   | french   | indonesian | malaysian |
| City         | hannover | prague | hamburg |

