.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda, tea
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, november, july
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking mirinda and the person who's birthday is in november##7
3. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Beverage   | mirinda      | tea     | almond-milk |
| Birthday        | july | january | november    |

 